Greg Serano https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Greg_Serano 0 Greg Serano (born August 7, 1974) is an American actor. He is best known for his role of Pablo Betart on Wildfire and as Enrique Salvatore in Legally Blonde. He played a role in Power as Agent Juan Julio Medina.
